On initial checkout do the following:
   autoreconf -fvi

Then to build:
1. Configure:
      ./configure --with-ampl=/path/to/amplsolver/dir
   If you wish to use the oops interface you will also need to supply the
   directories of MeTiS (--with-metis=path) and OOPS (--with-oops=path).
   The MPS interface can be diabled with the option --with-mps=no
2. Build:
      make
3. Install:
      make install
